---
The HTML backup is created every time you close Firefox
1. access about:config with firefox.
2. change the set "browser.bookmarks.autoExportHTML" as "true".
3. create the string pref "browser.bookmarks.file" with the full path including the file name.(e.g. browser.bookmarks.file = /home/elm/elm_workstation/firefox_bookmarks/bookmarks.html)

---
1.
$ sudo find / -name ".mozilla"
